Method Detail

getMetadata

String getMetadata(Long projectCode,
                   Long bookingId,
                   String destinationURL)
Returns metadata from booking system accociated with the provided project and booking. If projectCode and/or bookingId is null or no metadata for the provided parameters can be found then metadata skeleton (template with empty field values) is returned.

Parameters:
projectCode - project code in the booking system
bookingId - booking ID
destinationURL - URL of datasets this metadata should be associated with
Returns:
xml string of metadata (in RIF-CS format for example)

getMetadata

String getMetadata(Map<String,Object> params)
Returns metadata populated with the provided parameters

Parameters:
params - map of parameters to populate. Key is parameter name (place holder in the template), Value is parameter value (Can be string or list/array of strings).
Returns:
